{"word":"ἀργύριον","slug":"ἀργύριον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀργύριον, ου, τό</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἄργυρος\">ἄργυρος</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> the precious metal known as <b><i>silver</i> <a href='B:530 3:12'>1 Cor 3:12</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp> <i>silver</i></b> as medium of exchange<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> with focus on the precious metal in the medium of exchange <b><a href='B:510 3:6'>Ac 3:6</a>; <a href='B:510 7:16'>7:16</a>; <a href='B:510 20:33'>20:33</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:670 1:18'>1 Pt 1:18</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> a specific monetary unit: <i>silver shekel</i> <b><a href='B:470 26:15'>Mt 26:15</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prob.\">prob.</a> <i>silver</i> <i>drachma</i> <b><a href='B:510 19:19'>Ac 19:19</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> in general = <i>money</i> <b><a href='B:470 25:18'>Mt 25:18</a>, <a href='B:470 25:27'>27</a>; <a href='B:480 14:11'>Mk 14:11</a>; <a href='B:490 9:3'>Lk 9:3</a>; <a href='B:490 19:15'>19:15</a>, <a href='B:490 19:23'>23</a>; <a href='B:490 22:5'>22:5</a>; <a href='B:510 8:20'>Ac 8:20</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀργύρεος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀργυροκόπος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}